data.description: NEW Year! New HOME! New investment property! This wonderful two-story home has many updates including NEW Furnace, new custom shelving, NEW ROOF, new gas lines and much more. Spacious eat in kitchen with large laundry room conveniently located off to the side. You will love the large bathroom, space for extra linen closet. All appliances included with washer and dryer. This is the deal of the year. Possibility of extra bedroom downstairs. Set your appointment today to see this wonderfully spacious home with side screened in porch. Agents, please see extra details in listing.
